Potem w kodzie zamień:

queries_dir = params["sql_paths"]["queries_dir"]

na:

from config import settings
queries_dir = settings.SQL_QUERIES_DIR

oraz:

sql_paths = common["sql_paths"]
schema_dir = sql_paths["schema_dir"]
views_dir = sql_paths["views_dir"]
indexes_dir = sql_paths["indexes_dir"]

na:

from config import settings
schema_dir = settings.SQL_SCHEMA_DIR
views_dir = settings.SQL_VIEWS_DIR
indexes_dir = settings.SQL_INDEXES_DIR

I dla Excela:

multi_client_excel_path = params["multi_client_excel_path"]

zamień na:

multi_client_excel_path = settings.MULTI_CLIENT_EXCEL_PATH

albo bezpieczniej tymczasowo:

multi_client_excel_path = settings.MULTI_CLIENT_EXCEL_PATH or params.get("multi_client_excel_path")

Po tych zmianach możesz usunąć z config.yaml:

sql_paths:
  schema_dir: "sql/schema"
  views_dir: "sql/views"
  indexes_dir: "sql/indexes"
  queries_dir: "sql/queries"

oraz docelowo także:

multi_client_excel_path: './data/input/Bartek_dane_20260429.xlsx'

ale to drugie usuń dopiero, gdy kod już bierze settings.MULTI_CLIENT_EXCEL_PATH.